{center}
{subhead}The Ottawa Amiga Show 2001, hosted by Amiga.info{def}
{left}
{pp}
The Ottawa Amiga Show will be held on Saturday, November 17 (11:00 AM to
5:00 PM) and Sunday November 18, 2001 (11:00 AM to 4:00PM), at the 
Travelodge Hotel (formerly known as the Talisman) on 1376 Carling Avenue 
in Ottawa, Canada. 
{pp}
The show will feature the latest Amiga operating system, software titles,
games, hardware, and more! Admission to the show is only $2.00 a person per day. Everyone is welcome! 
{pp}
The Ottawa Amiga Show is sponsored by Technomages and Cinereal Pro
Video.{p}
All prices listed on this website are in Canadian funds.{p}
Web Site Contents (Updated October 2, 2001){p}
